    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features of the current DEMO</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer:</strong> Battle against your friends on the same couch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vs CPU</strong>: Train your skills in a single-player experience vs the CPU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 Playable Characters</strong>: Zer0 and Slice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Stages</strong>: Ziggurat, Data Center, and Training Room</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 Terrains</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Street Fighter meets Nidhogg in the best game to introduce fighting games to your friends that don't play fighting games. Cross the goal to win the match, use the platforms to position yourself strategically, react quickly, KO your opponent, and run as fast as you can. Rollback Netcode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/7cd125ffa17150cc4b1cfb03402076da.poster.avif?t=1770285217\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/7cd125ffa17150cc4b1cfb03402076da.webm?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/7cd125ffa17150cc4b1cfb03402076da.mp4?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Platforms add a new dimension to strategic positioning. Read, react and trick your opponent</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Position yourself strategically to get the advantage</strong>. Knock out your opponent by breaking their guard with your combos, punish them at the right moment or trick them using throws, pokes, and cross-ups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/3a00683b13737957ea35f740f4f61235.poster.avif?t=1770285217\" width=606 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/3a00683b13737957ea35f740f4f61235.webm?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/3a00683b13737957ea35f740f4f61235.mp4?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make combos and special attacks without bleeding your thumb</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters are controlled only with directions and two attack buttons, making the game very <strong>easy to learn</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Training execution for days before playing online is not needed for this game. Go straight to the fun playing the mind game of fighting games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/230d7d787c78aed32d4dee3b6a050e99.poster.avif?t=1770285217\" width=610 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/230d7d787c78aed32d4dee3b6a050e99.webm?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/230d7d787c78aed32d4dee3b6a050e99.mp4?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cross the goal and win the match!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat</strong> your opponent, <strong>run</strong> fast as possible and <strong>cross the goal</strong> at the end of the stage to win the match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/b06fe45afc5092f77e2d7233d7cdffd6.poster.avif?t=1770285217\" width=608 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/b06fe45afc5092f77e2d7233d7cdffd6.webm?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386130/extras/b06fe45afc5092f77e2d7233d7cdffd6.mp4?t=1770285217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn fighting game concepts by playing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't know what cross-counter, priority, or cross-up hits are? Don't worry! The game will show you them as they happen, and you'll learn by playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rollback netcode ensures a responsive low latency gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Planned Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong>: An amazing single-player experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer:</strong> Battle against your friends on the same couch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Playable Characters</strong> across <strong>3 Unique Factions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Stages</strong> designed for intense battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40+ Terrains </strong>offering diverse strategic gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rollback Netcode Multiplayer</strong> for smooth, cross-platform online play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay tuned for updates as we bring this vision to life!</p>",
